data.description: Every once in a while a Stunning Home with a rare location becomes available for sale! This property is located in a Gated Community in Galena Forest and is adjacent to open-space and a seasonal creek. The beautiful environment makes for a very private and serene setting.  Upon entering the home, you’ll be “wowed” by the grand feel of the sunlit rooms brightened through the large windows with high ceilings.  Views from almost every window add to the serene feel of this special property. This home features 4 bedrooms, private Office with built-ins, 4.5 bathrooms and a 4 car garage.  The Primary Suite is on the main level with a private sitting area, 3-sided gas fireplace and two walk-in closets. The spa bathroom has double sinks, a walk in dual person shower and jetted tub.  A Fabulous Chefs Gourmet Kitchen awaits your culinary experience and Includes a Sub-Zero side by side Refrigerator/Freezer, 2- Bosch Dishwashers, Prep Island with separate sink, and second Bosch Dishwasher and garbage disposal, in addition to a Dacor 6 Burner Gas Stove and Dual Electric Ovens, Dacor warming drawer & Dacor Microwave and a Thermadoor commercial oven Hood/Vent.  The Great room has an impressive 48” Xtrordinair, marble-faced with Mantel gas fireplace and floor to ceiling windows to enjoy nature, the forest and the seasonal creek. Great room includes dining room and a formal Bar with refrigerator and wine refrigerator, and granite counter tops - all perfect for entertaining.  From the Great room you can flow into the family room, for Media enjoyment or get cozy next to the 36” Xtrodinair gas fireplace with designer tiger wood mantel.  Upstairs are 3 ensuites all with custom stone bathrooms.  Newer features include:   Over 1400 square feet of “Sheoga” Character Hickory Wood engineered flooring installed in 2022, Dual-Zone programmable HVAC System with new whole house Dual-HEPA filtration system and separate whole house humidifier installed in 2022, lower level whole house Speaker system individually controlled room by room to include deck area and “Conrad" woven wood blinds in Media Room, primary bedroom , and three Additional Bedrooms.  The home has been meticulously maintained. The list of amenities and features is expansive! Please see MLS docs for a list of features. A Must See Home!
